00:45:05,729 --> 00:45:07,060
<font color="yellow">pernah mengalaminya.</font>

569
00:45:10,530 --> 00:45:12,200
<font color="yellow">Astaga, ada apa denganku?</font>

570
00:45:13,200 --> 00:45:14,939
<font color="yellow">Aku pasti kelilipan.</font>

571
00:46:15,430 --> 00:46:18,700
<font color="yellow">"Meloholic"</font>

572
00:46:19,899 --> 00:46:23,010
<font color="yellow">Kamu tertarik kepadaku atau tidak?</font>

573
00:46:23,169 --> 00:46:25,479
<font color="yellow">Akan kubantu agar kamu terlepas dari nasib sialmu.</font>

574
00:46:25,539 --> 00:46:29,680
