575
00:46:29,680 --> 00:46:30,680
<font color="yellow">Aku mencintaimu.</font>

576
00:46:30,680 --> 00:46:33,120
<font color="yellow">Aku memberimu begitu banyak sinyal.</font>

577
00:46:33,649 --> 00:46:36,390
<font color="yellow">Karena mantan kekasihmu? Apa kesalahanku?</font>

578
00:46:36,390 --> 00:46:37,850
<font color="yellow">Jangan jatuh cinta dengan orang sakit jiwa.</font>

579
00:46:37,850 --> 00:46:39,060
<font color="yellow">Hati-hati.</font>

580
00:46:39,060 --> 00:46:40,419
<font color="yellow">Han Ye Ri bisa membuatmu sial.</font>

581
00:46:40,419 --> 00:46:42,160
<font color="yellow">- Astaga. - Kamu sudah terkutuk.</font>

582
00:46:42,390 --> 00:46:44,689
<font color="yellow">Kurasa sebaiknya kamu memberi tahu dia segalanya.</font>

583
00:46:44,689 --> 00:46:46,959
<font color="yellow">Beri tahu soal hal buruk yang ada di dalam dirimu.</font>

584
00:46:46,959 --> 00:46:48,300
<font color="yellow">Sebaiknya aku mengakhirinya.</font>

585
00:46:48,470 --> 00:46:49,569
<font color="yellow">Bunuh diri.</font>

586
00:46:49,569 --> 00:46:51,200
<font color="yellow">Aku akan mengakhiri segalanya.</font>

587
00:46:51,200 --> 00:46:53,370
<font color="yellow">Han Ye Ri! Jangan!</font>

